1
00:01:08,400 --> 00:01:10,200
I disagree.

2
00:01:25,159 --> 00:01:27,760
Mr. Ke, the leaders are very dissatisfied

3
00:01:27,760 --> 00:01:29,560
with the exhibition.

4
00:01:30,079 --> 00:01:32,480
All the involved staff should be fired

5
00:01:32,879 --> 00:01:35,159
and bear the corresponding losses.

6
00:01:35,480 --> 00:01:37,079
A murder case happened in the museum.

7
00:01:37,079 --> 00:01:38,200
It's an emergency.

8
00:01:38,200 --> 00:01:40,120
It has nothing to do with our staff.

9
00:01:40,280 --> 00:01:41,799
The foundation should understand.

10
00:01:41,959 --> 00:01:44,000
Mr. Ke, we have discussed it.

11
00:01:44,040 --> 00:01:44,959
We did

12
00:01:44,959 --> 00:01:47,359
have some shortcomings in this exhibition.

13
00:01:47,359 --> 00:01:48,319
We can dismiss the staff,

14
00:01:48,319 --> 00:01:49,680
but we firmly disagree

15
00:01:49,680 --> 00:01:51,120
with bearing the loss.

16
00:01:51,319 --> 00:01:52,200
Mr. Ke,

17
00:01:52,920 --> 00:01:54,959
as the secretary of the headquarters of the Shan Yuan International,

18
00:01:54,959 --> 00:01:56,120
I'm here

19
00:01:56,319 --> 00:01:58,359
to convey the opinions of the senior management.

20
00:02:02,120 --> 00:02:03,719
You're just a secretary.

21
00:02:05,959 --> 00:02:08,319
Why don't you go and check the exhibits first?

22
00:02:08,759 --> 00:02:10,080
I'll talk to the headquarters

23
00:02:10,599 --> 00:02:11,759
of the foundation myself.

24
00:02:12,599 --> 00:02:13,599
That's fine.

25
00:02:20,639 --> 00:02:21,719
I asked you to come here

26
00:02:21,719 --> 00:02:22,879
because I'm afraid you won't believe me.

27
00:02:24,520 --> 00:02:26,039
Are you serious?

28
00:02:26,919 --> 00:02:28,199
How did you find the switch?

29
00:02:31,120 --> 00:02:32,680
I fell asleep in the workshop while fixing a jade.

30
00:02:32,919 --> 00:02:34,199
In my dream, my great-grandmother

31
00:02:34,560 --> 00:02:35,960
opened the passage

32
00:02:35,960 --> 00:02:36,960
to protect the revolutionaries.

33
00:02:38,120 --> 00:02:39,159
I followed her instructions,

34
00:02:40,680 --> 00:02:41,960
and then you knew the rest.

35
00:02:51,159 --> 00:02:53,479
So those two people in my dream

36
00:02:54,280 --> 00:02:56,680
were your great-grandparents?

37
00:02:57,719 --> 00:02:58,360
Yes.

38
00:02:59,319 --> 00:03:00,360
I just

39
00:03:00,960 --> 00:03:02,560
realized it recently.

40
00:03:05,800 --> 00:03:07,360
Have you ever thought that

41
00:03:08,120 --> 00:03:09,280
maybe

42
00:03:10,039 --> 00:03:10,960
it's fate?

43
00:03:13,280 --> 00:03:15,280
What kind of person was my great-grandmother?

44
00:03:16,360 --> 00:03:17,680
I think this mansion

45
00:03:19,639 --> 00:03:20,759
and this jade pendant

46
00:03:21,000 --> 00:03:22,680
contain their stories.

47
00:03:23,319 --> 00:03:24,919
I've never said it.

48
00:03:25,199 --> 00:03:26,560
I always felt

49
00:03:26,560 --> 00:03:28,680
the answer would gradually emerge on its own.

50
00:03:29,000 --> 00:03:29,840
Jiang Xun,

51
00:03:30,960 --> 00:03:32,360
some fates and clues

52
00:03:32,599 --> 00:03:33,879
naturally require time

53
00:03:33,879 --> 00:03:34,919
to come to you

54
00:03:34,919 --> 00:03:35,960
step by step.

55
00:03:39,039 --> 00:03:40,000
I'll see if you're a real playboy

56
00:03:40,000 --> 00:03:41,520
or just a fake.

57
00:03:42,879 --> 00:03:44,680
Then you'd better look carefully.

58
00:03:44,840 --> 00:03:46,120
Don't be fooled by me.

59
00:03:46,680 --> 00:03:47,439
Don't worry.

60
00:03:48,879 --> 00:03:50,000
I have

61
00:03:51,240 --> 00:03:52,400
a sharp eye.

62
00:03:55,680 --> 00:03:56,560
So, are you saying

63
00:03:57,360 --> 00:03:58,680
you'll be my girlfriend?

64
00:04:09,639 --> 00:04:10,879
Work comes first.

65
00:04:11,879 --> 00:04:12,800
As for dating,

66
00:04:13,360 --> 00:04:14,479
we can do it later.

67
00:04:15,680 --> 00:04:16,800
Go have fun on your own.

68
00:04:21,839 --> 00:04:23,800
Okay, I'll go explore by myself.

69
00:04:46,079 --> 00:04:47,560
Ke Yu'ang asked Jiang Xun

70
00:04:47,560 --> 00:04:49,600
to do pre-exhibition restoration of the relics.

71
00:04:50,240 --> 00:04:51,879
After the restoration was completed,

72
00:04:53,879 --> 00:04:55,199
the museum lost power,

73
00:04:55,439 --> 00:04:56,759
and Ke Yu'ang disappeared as well.

74
00:04:58,560 --> 00:04:59,680
Without evidence,

75
00:04:59,680 --> 00:05:01,240
are just suspicions.

76
00:05:03,079 --> 00:05:04,319
So many people

77
00:05:04,319 --> 00:05:05,680
are interested in this jade.

78
00:05:05,839 --> 00:05:06,680
Why?

79
00:05:10,079 --> 00:05:12,959
Legend says a jade fell when King Wu attacked Zhou.

80
00:05:13,279 --> 00:05:16,160
This jade symbolizes the victory of justice and order.

81
00:05:16,680 --> 00:05:18,879
Mr. Shen, you've come to the museum to buy jade.

82
00:05:19,240 --> 00:05:21,399
But you can't afford this jade.

83
00:05:38,800 --> 00:05:39,920
Lin Chuyi.

84
00:05:40,199 --> 00:05:41,360
It's her.

85
00:05:42,439 --> 00:05:43,040
Lady,

86
00:05:43,040 --> 00:05:44,240
do I know you?

87
00:05:45,279 --> 00:05:46,600
Cut the act.

88
00:05:46,959 --> 00:05:48,959
You may be known as a playboy now,

89
00:05:49,160 --> 00:05:50,439
but back in school,

90
00:05:50,439 --> 00:05:51,480
you were quite the romantic.

91
00:05:52,439 --> 00:05:54,040
I was never romantic.

92
00:05:54,079 --> 00:05:56,680
You've been a playboy since childhood.

93
00:05:56,839 --> 00:05:57,680
I really don't remember.

94
00:05:57,680 --> 00:05:58,920
You have to remind me.

95
00:05:59,600 --> 00:06:02,160
Well, let me formally introduce myself.

96
00:06:02,759 --> 00:06:05,639
I'm the secretary of the Shan Yuan International Charity Foundation.

97
00:06:05,800 --> 00:06:06,519
My name is

98
00:06:06,519 --> 00:06:07,959
Lin Chuyi.

99
00:06:08,279 --> 00:06:10,319
Do you remember now, Young Master Shen?

100
00:06:12,199 --> 00:06:13,040
I remember now.

101
00:07:45,240 --> 00:07:46,800
[Extra edition!]

102
00:07:47,160 --> 00:07:49,759
[Five communists were arrested last night in Zhiwu Alley]

103
00:07:49,759 --> 00:07:52,480
[and executed in the burial ground overnight.]

104
00:07:52,519 --> 00:07:53,480
[Extra edition!]

105
00:07:53,879 --> 00:07:54,560
Give me a copy.

106
00:07:54,800 --> 00:07:55,160
Okay.

107
00:07:56,759 --> 00:07:57,120
Here you are.

108
00:08:00,839 --> 00:08:01,680
Thank you.

109
00:08:01,800 --> 00:08:03,160
[Extra.]

110
00:08:03,160 --> 00:08:04,759
[The whereabouts of the communists were exposed.]

111
00:08:04,759 --> 00:08:06,519
[It is suspected that Jiang Song was the informant.]

112
00:08:06,759 --> 00:08:09,360
[Jiang Song is having an affair with a Japanese man.]

113
00:08:09,360 --> 00:08:10,720
[Extra.]

114
00:08:15,040 --> 00:08:17,160
You went to see him again behind my back?

115
00:08:20,879 --> 00:08:22,680
The whole Rongzhou has heard about it.

116
00:08:26,160 --> 00:08:27,279
Why didn't you explain?

117
00:08:28,600 --> 00:08:30,160
Why didn't you deny?

118
00:08:46,559 --> 00:08:47,679
Fine.

119
00:08:49,679 --> 00:08:51,159
I'll let you have your way.

120
00:09:24,360 --> 00:09:26,559
Why did Great-Grandma become a traitor?

121
00:09:27,399 --> 00:09:29,519
Why was there a divorce paper?

122
00:09:39,159 --> 00:09:41,799
Didn't you go abroad after high school?

123
00:09:41,799 --> 00:09:43,559
I remember the last time we were in touch

124
00:09:44,120 --> 00:09:46,519
was when you wrote to me

125
00:09:46,519 --> 00:09:48,080
from Caltech, right?

126
00:09:48,480 --> 00:09:50,279
What are you planning to do this time?

127
00:09:51,639 --> 00:09:52,879
The Hongcheng relics exhibition

128
00:09:52,879 --> 00:09:53,919
is a cultural project

129
00:09:53,919 --> 00:09:55,480
fully supported by our foundation.

130
00:09:57,399 --> 00:09:58,720
You must have heard about

131
00:09:58,720 --> 00:10:00,159
the incident at the museum.

132
00:10:00,360 --> 00:10:01,159
Of course.

133
00:10:01,679 --> 00:10:03,039
I'm here in Rongzhou

134
00:10:03,039 --> 00:10:03,879
to manage

135
00:10:03,879 --> 00:10:05,840
the public relations and sentiment.

136
00:10:08,240 --> 00:10:09,759
Here's my business card.

137
00:10:11,399 --> 00:10:14,200
Senior secretary of

138
00:10:14,600 --> 00:10:15,480
Shanyuan International Charity Foundation.

139
00:10:16,000 --> 00:10:17,559
Is your headquarters in Port City

140
00:10:17,559 --> 00:10:18,480
or Rongzhou?

141
00:10:18,840 --> 00:10:19,639
Port City.

142
00:10:21,480 --> 00:10:23,840
Besides the cultural industry,

143
00:10:23,840 --> 00:10:25,279
does your fund also invest in other industries?

144
00:10:26,159 --> 00:10:29,000
Old classmate, you're asking me so many questions.

145
00:10:29,200 --> 00:10:30,399
Aren't you afraid I'll think

146
00:10:30,399 --> 00:10:32,279
you're trying to get back together with me?

147
00:10:34,080 --> 00:10:35,279
We haven't seen each other for so many years.

148
00:10:35,279 --> 00:10:36,360
you don't invite me to dinner?

149
00:10:39,080 --> 00:10:39,919
Sorry.

150
00:10:43,000 --> 00:10:44,360
Is my girlfriend checking up on me?

151
00:10:45,240 --> 00:10:46,279
There's an emergency at home.

152
00:10:46,279 --> 00:10:47,240
I have to go.

153
00:10:47,240 --> 00:10:49,279
Let's keep in touch

154
00:10:49,279 --> 00:10:50,399
and catch up later.

155
00:10:50,600 --> 00:10:51,360
Okay?

156
00:10:51,360 --> 00:10:52,279
Bye.

157
00:11:29,440 --> 00:11:30,480
Although Lin Chuyi,

158
00:11:30,480 --> 00:11:32,159
the secretary of an international foundation,

159
00:11:32,159 --> 00:11:33,000
appears glamorous

160
00:11:33,200 --> 00:11:34,240
and sophisticated,

161
00:11:34,559 --> 00:11:35,440
but she harbors

162
00:11:35,440 --> 00:11:37,080
malicious intentions

163
00:11:37,080 --> 00:11:38,320
against our national security.

164
00:11:38,879 --> 00:11:39,639
In recent years,

165
00:11:39,639 --> 00:11:41,679
more and more foreign NGOs

166
00:11:41,679 --> 00:11:42,679
have come to our country,

167
00:11:42,799 --> 00:11:44,679
making positive contributions

168
00:11:44,679 --> 00:11:45,480
to promoting friendly exchanges

169
00:11:45,679 --> 00:11:46,879
between China and the world.

170
00:11:47,240 --> 00:11:49,279
But in the covert battlefield,

171
00:11:49,279 --> 00:11:51,440
foreign spies will also carry out infiltration, subversion and sabotage

172
00:11:51,440 --> 00:11:53,360
against our country

173
00:11:53,360 --> 00:11:55,960
through non-governmental organizations.

174
00:11:56,200 --> 00:11:57,759
We must be vigilant

175
00:11:57,840 --> 00:11:58,480
and not be deceived

176
00:11:58,480 --> 00:12:00,559
by seemingly noble identities.
